childrelationship.name: ChildRelationship
childrelationship.description: Contains methods for accessing the child relationship as well as the child sObject for a parent sObject.

datacategory.name: DataCategory
datacategory.description: Represents the categories within a category group.

datacategorygroupsobjecttypepair.name: DataCategoryGroupSobjectTypePair
datacategorygroupsobjecttypepair.description: Specifies a category group and an associated object.

describecolorresult.name: DescribeColorResult
describecolorresult.description: Contains color metadata information for a tab.

describedatacategorygroupresult.name: DescribeDataCategoryGroupResult
describedatacategorygroupresult.description: Contains the list of the category groups associated with KnowledgeArticleVersion and Question.

describedatacategorygroupstructureresult.name: DescribeDataCategoryGroupStructureResult
describedatacategorygroupstructureresult.description: Contains the category groups and categories associated with KnowledgeArticleVersion and Question.

describefieldresult.name: DescribeFieldResult
describefieldresult.description: Contains methods for describing sObject fields.

describeiconresult.name: DescribeIconResult
describeiconresult.description: Contains icon metadata information for a tab.

describetabresult.name: DescribeTabResult
describetabresult.description: Contains tab metadata information for a tab in a standard or custom app available in the Salesforce user interface.

describetabsetresult.name: DescribeTabSetResult
describetabsetresult.description: Contains metadata information about a standard or custom app available in the Salesforce user interface.

displaytype.name: DisplayType
displaytype.description: A Schema.DisplayType enum value is returned by the field describe result's getType method.

fieldset.name: FieldSet
fieldset.description: Contains methods for discovering and retrieving the details of field sets created on sObjects.

fieldsetmember.name: FieldSetMember
fieldsetmember.description: Contains methods for accessing the metadata for field set member fields.

recordtypeinfo.name: RecordTypeInfo
recordtypeinfo.description: Contains methods for accessing record type information for an sObject with associated record types.

soaptype.name: SOAPType
soaptype.description: A Schema.SOAPType enum value is returned by the field describe result getSoapType method.

sobjectfield.name: sObjectField
sobjectfield.description: A Schema.sObjectField object is returned from the field describe result using the getControler and getSObjectField methods.

sobjecttype.name: SObjectType
sobjecttype.description: A Schema.sObjectType object is returned from the field describe result using the getReferenceTo method, or from the sObject describe result using the getSObjectType method.
